  <shortlink>api a5 table size to fit dialog function</shortlink>
   <topic>A5_TableSizeToFit_Dialog Function</topic>
     <description>Displays the SizeTableToFit dialog box</description>
   <syntax>V a5_TableSizeToFit_Dialog([C tablename ])</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>tablename</name>
         <description>The name of a table.</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
 
   <discussion>
The A5_TableSizeToFit_Dialog() function displays the Size Fields to Fit dialog, which allows you to resize the table's field to fit its data.

   </discussion>
  <limitations>Desktop applications only.</limitations>
